Text: YEAR EXECUTIVE COMMUNICATIONS PLAN Cc find the final executive communications document with completed phone numbers for the millennium rollover weekend The YK Corporate team and all Enron business units will be monitoring the YK event the day prior to and following the rollover Each Enron major site has developed contingency plans and every Enron location will be contacted for status checks as the century rollover occurs We look forward to reporting our YK success
